g.text: Italians' self-reported depression is improving over time, while in Australia it took a hit around July. In New Zealand,
women rather than men reported more depression at the time of the outbreak around August.
University of Maryland Global Symptom Survey of Facebook users, analysed at http://freerangestats.info
